{"_id":"112383d36fc54406","name":"Ready an Action","type":"action","img":"icons/skills/melee/blade-damage.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"- **Cost:** 1 or 2\n- **Effect:** Choose a trigger and an action. When the trigger occurs before your next turn, you can use your [Reaction] to perform the readied action\n- **Examples:**\n  - \"I ready an attack for when the orc comes through the door\" (1 action)\n  - \"I ready a Fireball for when enemies cluster together\" (2 actions)\n- **Notes:**\n  - You must specify the trigger clearly\n  - If trigger doesn't occur, the action is lost\n  - Performing the readied action uses your [Reaction]\n  - Readied weaves that aren't used still consume Energy"},"actionType":"combat","actionCost":"1","trigger":"","effect":"Choose a trigger and an action. When the trigger occurs before your next turn, you can use your [Reaction] to perform the readied action\n- **Examples:**\n  - \"I ready an attack for when the orc comes through the door\" (1 action)\n  - \"I ready a Fireball for when enemies cluster together\" (2 actions)\n- **Notes:**\n  - You must specify the trigger clearly\n  - If trigger doesn't occur, the action is lost\n  - Performing the readied action uses your [Reaction]\n  - Readied weaves that aren't used still consume Energy","keywords":"Reaction","range":"","target":"","frequency":"","special":""},"effects":[],"_key":"!items!112383d36fc54406"}
